= DYI Changelog

== Version 1.3.0 / 2012-06-01
* Major Enhancement
  * Can draw a predefined shape.
  * Radial gradient support.
* Minor Enhancement
  * Adds options to LineChart.
  * Changes project URL.
  * Adds method that draws logomark of DYI.
* Bug Fixes
  * Revises spell-miss in DYI::Element#add_css_class.

== Version 1.2.1 / 2012-05-01
* Bug Fixes
  * A name of marker-option of LineChart is wrong.
  * A create option name of Text is wrong.
  * An operation of the link element.

== Version 1.2.0 / 2012-04-02
* Minor Enhancement
  * Marker support.
  * LineChart support markers.
* Bug Fixes
  * Factory method of Animation is invalid.
  * Event handers are not attached properly.

== Version 1.1.2 / 2012-03-01
* Bug Fixes
  * Calls data_label_format property instead of baloon_format when it draws the baloon of PieChart.
  * Changes the order of overlapping charts of LineChart.
  * Calcuration of second-axis settings of LineChart.

== Version 1.1.1 / 2012-02-02
* Minor Enhancements
  * Adds a String parsing to CsvReader.
  * Spports metadata.
  * Adds 'title' and 'description' attribute to DYI::Element.

== Version 1.1.0 / 2012-01-06
* Major Enhancements
  * Adds DYI::Util module
  * Can draw a toroid.
  * Adds properties of PieChart.
  * Supports namespace on XML output.
  * Supports Inline-XML mode.

== Version 1.0.3 / 2011-11-27
* Bug Fixes
  * DataReader is not working properly in Ruby 1.9.
  * A ECMAScript function dose not work properly.

== Version 1.0.2 / 2011-09-30
* Bug Fixes
  * Initialization script can not register more than one.

== Version 1.0.1 / 2011-09-28
* Bug Fixes
  * A event listeners dose not work properly.
  * CSS class name is not outputed properly.

== Version 1.0.0 / 2011-09-05

* Major Enhancements
  * Supports events on SVG.
  * Supports animations on SVG.
  * Supports scripts (ex. ECMAScript) on SVG.
  * Supports hyperlinks on SVG.
  * Supports a SVG file that includes style-sheet (ex. CSS, XLST).
  * Supports PNG output. (Needs rsvg-convert)
  * Supports raster image handling (ex. PNG, JPEG) on SVG.
  * Adds Pie-Chart options.
  * Modifies the handling of Reader classes.

== Version 0.0.2 / 2011-09-05

* Minor Enhancements
  * Modifies header comments of output file.

* Bug Fixes
  * A path is not drawn correctly.
  * Miter length is not set corrently.

== Version 0.0.1 / 2011-07-15

* Bug Fixes
  * Clipping is not possible for a shape object.
  * A path is not drawn correctly.

== Version 0.0.0 / 2011-06-30

* First public release
